      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"start anew\"? how? the foundation of everything i know was wrong. i can't just pivot to a new career or \"start over\" when the very essence of my identity was built on a mistake. it feels like the character i've been playing for a decade just died. there's no version of the future where i'm not just a walking lie. it's exhausting to even breathe when you realize you've been living a fantasy.",
